OL,4,G1850FLocation, Location, Location
OL,5,     GKirstie Allsopp helps Andy and
OL,6,     GJenny search for their first home
OL,7,     Gnear Warrington. Phil Spencer is
OL,8,     Gwith Margot, who hopes to find a
OL,9,     Gforever home in the seaside town
OL,10,     Gof Crosby.
OL,11,G1955FKirstie and Phil's Love It or
OL,12,     FList It
OL,13,     GIn the village of Clifford,
OL,14,     GKirstie and Phil meet Vic and
OL,15,     GPaul. From the outside, their
OL,16,     Gidyllic home looks perfect for a
OL,17,     Gfamily, but appearances can be
OL,18,     Gdeceptive.
OL,19,G2100FGrand Designs
OL,20,     GKara and Jonny build a stone and
OL,21,     Gzinc home in West Yorkshire's
OL,22,     Ghills, facing tough challenges.
